1:
Yahweh reigns; he is robed in majesty;\q Yahweh has clothed and girded himself with strength.
\q The world is firmly established; it cannot be moved.
\q
2:
Your throne is established from ancient times;\q you are from everlasting.


\q
4:
Above the crashing of many waves,\q the mighty breakers of the sea,
\q Yahweh on high is mighty.


\q
5:
Your solemn commands are very trustworthy;\q holiness adorns your house,
\q Yahweh, forever.
